item.title: Herschel Observations of Plutinos
item.description: My first research paper. Using Herschel Space Observatory observations, we investigated the physical properties of 18 Plutinos - small bodies at the outskirts of the Solar System that have orbital properties similar to those of Pluto. What we found? That Pluto is pretty unique…
